| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5911 — Recovery Inhibition (funksec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8284d4ed-8f08-5a08-b6aa-5c396aad2e8c"
